    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level is considered medium due to the potential involvement of multiple calculations or data retrieval operations from one or more tables to compute the total energy usage. The function may involve conditional logic or aggregation operations that add to its complexity."
